sys_app_template_detail.author: ServiceNow
sys_app_template_detail.detailed_description: A way for users to access your app's info from one of your company's iOS or Android apps. If you'd like to add custom roles to this experience, create a role in Security. Once you create it, this role will show up as an option for you to select.
sys_app_template_detail.short_description: A way for users to access your app's info from a mobile device.
